snippet.title: Lost in the Dark Woods - Launch Trailer [OFFICIAL]
snippet.description:
You are lost in a dark forest, dangers lurk in every corner, a small hearth seems to be the only hope, you will have to feed it to try to survive.

The game download can be found on GameJolt or Itch.io.
So if you want to adventure search for "Lost in the Dark Woods" Game on Gamejolt

Remember:
The game is in early access and anything you see may be changed in the future
